description: The forms and publications resource page, the official source of IRS tax products. The links provide methods to access and acquire both electronic and print media. Additionally, the Search function provides basic and advanced search capabilities for published products available on IRS.gov.Individual and business taxpayers recently advised they will no longer receive income tax packages in the mail from the IRS can use the links on this page to view, download, or order the forms, schedules, and instructions needed for filing a paper income tax return.
